The following allows you to modify the emails generated automatically by the system.

<ol id="system-emails">
	<li><a href="admin/emails/edit/3">New customer account creation</a><br />
	Sent when a customer creates a new account.</li>
	<li><a href="admin/emails/edit/4">Order confirmation</a><br />
	Sent when an order is placed by a customer.</li>
	<li><a href="admin/emails/edit/5">Order status change</a><br />
	Sent when an administrator updates an orders status.</li>
	<li><a href="admin/emails/edit/1">Customer password renewal</a><br />
	Sent when a customer forgets their password and has it renewed.</li>
	<li><a href="admin/emails/edit/2">Store enquiry</a><br />
	Sent when a user makes a store enquiry via the contact us form.</li>
	<li><a href="admin/emails/edit/6">Activate E-Mail address</a><br />
	Sent when a user requires a new activation E-Mail sent.</li>
</ol>